title: Added Socket transport
message:
Added Socket transport

Changed NurDeviceSpec to use semicolan separated string w/ key/val pairs
as type/connection string. E.g.
"type=TCP;addr=127.0.0.1:4333;port=4333;name=DevName" or
"type=BLE;addr=xx:xx:xx:xx:xx:xx;name=DevName;bonded=false;rssi=-44"
